MM8DRead - Status reader program for MM8D device
------------------------------------------------

1. About software
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
  You can check status of MM8D growing house controllers with this
software via network.

2. How to get installer package for my OS?
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
a. Visit homepage (see later) to download installer packages:

  architecture  operation system        filename
  --------------------------------------------------------------------
  (all)         (source code)           mm8dread-0.4.tar.gz
  amd64         Linux                   mm8dread_0.4-1_amd64.deb
  amd64         Linux                   mm8dread-0.4-amd64.bin
  amd64         Linux                   mm8dread-0.4-amd64.tar.gz
  i386          Debian GNU/Linux        mm8dread_0.4-1_i386.deb
  i586          Linux                   mm8dread-0.4-i586.bin
  i586          Linux                   mm8dread-0.4-i586.tar.gz
  i586          Windows 32 bit          mm8dread-0.4-win32.exe
  i586          Windows 32 bit          mm8dread-0.4-win32.msi
  i586          Windows 32 bit          mm8dread-0.4-win32.zip

The source package can be compiled for arm, i386 and amd64 processors,
FreeBSD, Linux and Windows operating systems. The source package also
contains the necessary files for packaging.

b. Download from Github

  $ git clone https://github.com/pozsarzs/mm8dread.git

c. Download from Debian repository

  set reporitory:
  # echo "deb http://www.szerafingomba.hu/deb/ ./" >> /etc/apt/sources.list
  # wget -q -O - http://www.szerafingomba.hu/deb/KEY.gpg | apt-key add -
  # apt-get update

  install
  # apt-get install mm8dread

